---------
POSTGRESQL
---------

Show users: 
\du

Add user:
CREATE USER my_user WITH PASSWORD 'myPassword';

Grant privileges:
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON DATABASE dbname to my_user;



-----
MYSQL
-----
Show users:
SELECT * from mysql.user;

Add user:
CREATE USER 'my_user'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'some_pass';

Grant privileges:
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON my_database.* TO 'my_user'@'localhost';

Check privileges:
SHOW GRANTS FOR 'my_user'@'localhost';

